{"tid":312970,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[心得] 寧讀 IVE 不讀 ASSO！","createTime":"2017-07-08T02:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T08:18:54.000Z","uid":28614,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de712125eee61444db02906749f5c0a4ca7fd2d4","tid":312970,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:36:35.000Z","msg":"本人係今屆青衣 IVE Civil 畢業生，GPA 過 3.7 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收到哂 港大 科大 理大 土木工程既 admission offer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n亦都有同學 HKCC 2.6x 轉過黎 IVE Civil，依家 GPA 3.6x 準備入科大 Civil <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入 IVE 唔入 ASSO 既原因有三<br />\n<br />\n1. IVE 易讀，ASSO 2.x 既你係 IVE 一定過 3.0<br />\n<br />\n2. 大學不會分開 IVE ASSO 收生，即係 IVE 3.6 = ASSO 3.6 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> IVE 易高分有優勢<br />\n<br />\n3. IVE 重實際，ATAL 金門 等大公司每年大手買入 IVE 仔，畢業不愁搵工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nASSO 仔畢業連實物都未見過，仲要讀一大堆無用既通識科，畢業 = 失業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d9a5bcdf3a5c564d2824c3708d38378a3731b8","tid":312970,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01aa964812d3051fc86ebba228041f803929f47","tid":312970,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"間間CC都博命派grade 有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041dc6a3955734cfc838991dd79b6bbfa124531f","tid":312970,"uid":91244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T04:44:23.000Z","msg":"In 青大 we trust"},{"pid":"ad484c5235cb91218da7b4a87d0975ed2798e813","tid":312970,"uid":120051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕對係"}]}